pages.text: Anna Maria Island's Premier Wedding & Event Venue. Dream location with award winning chefs & mixologists to make your event truly special.

The Doctor’s Office
Great Food. Amazing Cocktails.
We offer three serving areas:
The Bar
– suited to the serious cocktail enthusiast on stool and high top seating and dining at tables proximate to the main bar area.
This is our most precious reservation area and offers a more extensive cocktail and spirits list.
The Doctor’s Garden
– for parties enthused about dining and cocktailing outside in a truly remarkable and even soothing garden environment, out-of-doors under the lights.
The Dining Room
– a smaller, more intimate seating area adjacent to the garden but removed from the vicissitudes of the elements.
The Bar areas are 21+ with Valid ID, and are not available to parties larger than eight.
The Garden and Dining Room are available for parties of eight or more.
Any party larger than 10 should make special arrangements by phone.
Any of our spaces are available for booking private events. This should be discussed with our managers.
We seat walk-ups depending on seating availability.
Reservations the “day of” your intended visit can be made by call us at 941-213-9926.
Children are welcome in all dining areas except the Bar Room.
We have a “Maturity Challenged” menu. We offer complimentary fresh fruit and berries to the children upon seating to help adjust their blood sugar and ameliorate their tendencies to become marauding heathens.
Vegan and Vegetarian offerings are available from the menu, on our daily specials list, and through discourse with the wait staff.
Most menu items are gluten free.
We would ask patrons to notify wait staff of any allergies immediately upon being seated.
Located on Anna Maria Island
Enjoy the best drinks, culinary offerings, and libations.
Reservations suggested, simply call
(941) 213-9926
.
